{% comment %} Privacy Policy Page {% endcomment %}

<style>
.policy-page { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 20px; }
.policy-page h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; }
.policy-page h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #ff6b9d; margin: 30px 0 15px; font-weight: 600; }
.policy-page p, .policy-page li { color: #555; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; }
.policy-page ul { padding-left: 20px; }
</style>

<div class="policy-page">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <p>At CatFat India, we value your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Personal information (name, email, phone, address) when you place an order</li>
    <li>Payment information (processed securely through our payment partners)</li>
    <li>Order history and preferences</li>
    <li>Communication data when you contact us</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To process and deliver your orders</li>
    <li>To communicate with you about order status</li>
    <li>To provide customer support</li>
    <li>To send promotional offers (with your consent)</li>
    <li>To improve our products and services</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Protection</h2>
  <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. Your payment information is encrypted and processed securely through certified payment gateways.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Sharing</h2>
  <p>We may share your information with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Delivery partners to ship your orders</li>
    <li>Payment gateways for transaction processing</li>
    <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Access your personal data</li>
    <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
    <li>Opt-out of promotional communications</li>
    <li>Data portability</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

  <h2>Changes to Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>For privacy concerns, contact us at info@catfat.in</p>
</div>

